These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, lemon, lime, grapefruit
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, fish, hamster, horse
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, helicopter, boat, roller
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
2. the person driving the roller is the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
4. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the fish is between the person driving the boat and the person eating lemon##2
6. the person driving the helicopter is the owner of the hamster##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | lime | grapefruit  | lemon | cucumber  |
| Pet         | horse    | fish  | rabbit       | hamster     |
| Transport   | boat     | ship | roller       | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, filmmaking, rock-climbing, puzzles
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, disaster, thriller, family
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, badminton, cricket, skateboarding
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person watching family movies and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
5. the person watching family movies is the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
7. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | gardening    | puzzles  | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | scientific  | disaster   | thriller    |
| Sport         | badminton | skateboarding | rowing | cricket      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, iced-tea, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, magic-tricks, writing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, r&b, disco, pop
1. the fan of r&b is between the fan of pop and the person drinking fanta##2
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left##1
6. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the fan of disco is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | fanta | soy-milk         | hot-chocolate   | iced-tea    |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | writing | camping | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | r&b        | pop      | salsa   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, malaysian, american, canadian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, swimming, baseball, weightlifting
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, tram, taxi, quad-bike
1. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the quad-bike and the canadian##2
3. the american is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the american is on the right of the argentine##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person driving the tram##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | canadian        | malaysian   | argentine | american |
| Sport         | baseball | surfing | swimming    | weightlifting |
| Transport     | taxi       | helicopter     | quad-bike       | tram    |

