.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, coffee, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, writing, chess, cooking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, rugby, skateboarding, baseball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person drinking water and the person drinking iced-tea##2
2. the person who's sport is baseball is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
7. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's hobby is collecting##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | water | sprite      | iced-tea       | coffee   |
| Hobby      | collecting   | writing  | cooking | chess     |
| Sport      | rugby     | baseball | skateboarding        | tennis |

