.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, carrot, kiwi, avocado
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, dancing, chess, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, parkour, water-polo, snowboarding
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person eating potato is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person eating potato is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
6. the person eating carrot is between the person eating potato and the person eating kiwi##2
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | kiwi | carrot  | potato | avocado      |
| Hobby   | chess  | writing  | filmmaking | dancing |
| Sport   | snowboarding | volleyball | parkour | water-polo     |

