The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, romance, comedy, thriller
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, sailing, golf, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
5. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the person eating eggplant is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching comedy movies##2
7. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | nectarine  | eggplant    | asparagus | spinach  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | thriller       | romance        | time-travel    |
| Sport         | sailing | snowboarding | rowing  | golf |

