.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, drawing, collecting, singing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, disaster, time-travel, satire
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rat, cat, bird
1. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is between the owner of the bird and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | singing  | drawing | collecting | gardening |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts  | satire | disaster   | time-travel         |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | cat  | rat   | bird      |

