.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, cucumber, asparagus, corn
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, traveling, drawing, puzzles
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, soul, classical, metal
1. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of metal##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person eating grapefruit##1
3. the fan of soul is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person eating cucumber##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating corn##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the fan of classical and the person who's hobby is board-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | corn  | grapefruit    | asparagus | cucumber       |
| Hobby         | puzzles | traveling | board-games  | drawing |
| Music-Genre   | classical   | metal      | soul  | r&b     |

