.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, grapefruit, lemon, tomato
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, fishing, writing, card-games
4 different pets are kept: mouse, chinchilla, snake, frog
1. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating lime##1
2. the owner of the snake is the person eating grapefruit##1
3. the owner of the mouse is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is writing##2
4. the person who's hobby is writing is between the owner of the mouse and the person eating tomato##2
5. the person who's hobby is writing is the owner of the frog##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | tomato  | lemon | lime | grapefruit     |
| Hobby   | cooking | writing   | card-games  | fishing    |
| Pet     | chinchilla        | frog       | mouse      | snake |

