.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, cola, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, photography, woodworking, magic-tricks
4 different pets are kept: fish, rat, guinea-pig, dog
1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking cola and the person who's hobby is photography##2
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
6. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | cola     | iced-tea | water       |
| Hobby      | woodworking  | magic-tricks | singing  | photography |
| Pet        | dog  | rat      | guinea-pig        | fish      |

