.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, accountant, security-guard, nurse
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, thriller, action
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, scooter, tram, subway
1. the person watching epic movies is the person driving the subway##1
2. the person driving the tram is the security-guard##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the freelancer##1
4. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the scooter is between the person watching thriller movies and the security-guard##2
6. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the scooter is the nurse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job           | accountant | nurse | security-guard    | freelancer   |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller      | martial-arts   | action | epic |
| Transport     | boat     | scooter       | tram        | subway    |

