.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, video-games, sudoku, photography
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, fisherman, designer, firefighter
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, golf, ice-hockey, baseball
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is the firefighter##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is between the journalist and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
6. the designer is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is golf##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Hobby   | sudoku   | video-games           | board-games         | photography      |
| Job     | journalist | designer | firefighter | fisherman |
| Sport   | ice-hockey     | golf         | cycling       | baseball        |

