.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, coffee, milk, juice
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, jazz, d&b, disco
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, argentine, polish, french
1. the fan of punk is the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking milk and the argentine##2
3. the person drinking milk is the fan of jazz##1
4. the person drinking milk is between the fan of d&b and the french##2
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
6. the australian is between the polish and the fan of disco##2
7. the fan of punk is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee | milk | fanta   | juice |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | jazz    | d&b   | disco     |
| Nationality   | french  | polish | australian | argentine   |

