.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, 7up, juice
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, watermelon, tomato, grapes
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, soccer, ice-hockey, skiing
1. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
2. the person eating tomato is between the person drinking juice and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
7. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | water    | iced-tea | juice           | 7up |
| Food       | grapefruit | tomato    | watermelon          | grapes   |
| Sport      | ice-hockey  | soccer   | skiing | sailing  |

