.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, 7up, lemonade
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, thriller, fantasy, comedy
4 different pets are kept: rat, ferret, dog, bird
1. the person watching fantasy movies is the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching musical movies##2
5. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the owner of the bird is between the person drinking coffee and the owner of the rat##2
7. the person watching comedy movies is the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | 7up | iced-tea | coffee     | lemonade   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | comedy        | fantasy  | thriller  |
| Pet           | rat      | bird         | ferret | dog |

