.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-19::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, entrepreneur, scientist, dressmaker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, handball, biathlon, rugby
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, skateboard, motorbike, bike
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the scientist##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is the person driving the car##1
3. the police-officer is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is the dressmaker##1
5. the person who's sport is climbing is the person driving the motorbike##1
6. the person driving the bike is between the person who's sport is handball and the person driving the motorbike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | police-officer        | dressmaker  | scientist | entrepreneur   |
| Sport       | rugby | climbing | biathlon    | handball |
| Transport   | car        | motorbike     | bike       | skateboard      |

