.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, pumpkin, raspberry, apricot
4 different pets are kept: pony, dog, goldfish, ferret
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, van, tram, train
1. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the person driving the van is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the train is the owner of the ferret##1
6. the owner of the dog is between the person eating apricot and the person driving the tram##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | apricot | pumpkin | grapefruit | raspberry |
| Pet         | pony       | dog     | goldfish   | ferret   |
| Transport   | subway | van | tram | train |

 